    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 credibility matrix. The CFD model is judged sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device, with RHI predictions validated against the FDA benchmark dataset within acceptable uncertainty bounds. The relative hemolysis index at worst-case conditions satisfies RH < 1 relative to the predicate device. The assessment team accepts the model for its intended use.",
